&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A proprietary development by RailTech — a digital B2B platform that automates the full industrial equipment supply cycle.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h3 class="relative group"&gt;Key Modules
 &lt;div id="key-modules" class="anchor"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
 
 &lt;span
 class="absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none"&gt;
 &lt;a class="text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline" href="#key-modules" aria-label="Anchor"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
 &lt;/span&gt;
 
&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Catalog&lt;/strong&gt; — 500+ items from 86 manufacturers with technical documentation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Quote Calculator&lt;/strong&gt; — automatic Landed Cost computation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;CRM&lt;/strong&gt; — deal management and document workflow&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Partner Portal&lt;/strong&gt; — partner workspace with KYC verification&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Smart Import&lt;/strong&gt; — Excel upload with automatic item matching&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Admin Panel&lt;/strong&gt; — system-wide monitoring and management&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;h3 class="relative group"&gt;Technology
 &lt;div id="technology" class="anchor"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
 
 &lt;span
