&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The platform is built on a modern technology stack, ensuring high performance, security, and scalability.&lt;/p&gt;</description><media:content xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://nzulkaynarov.github.io/rt-website-public/en/projects/b2b-platform/featured.jpg"/></item><item><title>RailTech Launches B2B Platform for Industrial Procurement</title><link>https://nzulkaynarov.github.io/rt-website-public/en/blog/b2b-platform-launch/</link><pubDate>Sun, 15 Sep 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://nzulkaynarov.github.io/rt-website-public/en/blog/b2b-platform-launch/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;RailTech has launched its proprietary digital B2B platform, automating the full cycle of industrial equipment supply in Uzbekistan.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h2 class="relative group"&gt;Platform Capabilities
 &lt;div id="platform-capabilities" class="anchor"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
 
 &lt;span
 class="absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none"&gt;
 &lt;a class="text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline" href="#platform-capabilities" aria-label="Anchor"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
 &lt;/span&gt;
 
&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The platform integrates a catalog of 500+ equipment items, a quote calculator with Landed Cost computation, a CRM system for deal management, and a Partner Portal with KYC verification.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The standout feature is &lt;strong&gt;Smart Import&lt;/strong&gt;, which allows users to upload an Excel file with their required items and automatically match them against the catalog. The algorithm achieves approximately 92% accuracy.&lt;/p&gt;

